      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/2/38/36",
      "text": [
        " \"تَصَدَّقُ عَنْ كُلِّ يَوْمٍ بِمُدٍّ مِنْ حِنْطَةٍ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4308 - Muhammad ibn Mansur asked Imam Musa ibn Jafar Al-Kadhim (as) about a man who made a vow to fast but found fasting to be too difficult for him.\nImam (as) said: \"He should give charity for each day in the amount of one mudd of wheat.\""
        ]
      }
